coma</li><li>Generalized nbrocystic disease (von Recklinghausen)</li><li>Fracture</li><li>Acquired syphilitic disease of bone</li><li>Paget''s disease (in the upper years of age-group)</li><li>Acromegaly</li><li>Myeloma</li><li>Metastitic tumours</li></ul>', 'B'),
